code: import os import pandas as pd import numpy as np from sklearn.model_selection import StratifiedKFold from sklearn.metrics import roc_auc_score import torch from torch import nn import torch.optim as optim from torch.utils.data import DataLoader, Dataset from torchvision import transforms import timm from tqdm import tqdm from PIL import Image # Configuration BATCH_SIZE = 32 IMG_SIZE = 384 EPOCHS = 2 FOLDS = 2 SEED = 42 # Data preparation train_df = pd.read_csv("./input/train.csv") test_files = os.listdir("./input/test") # Create stratified folds skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=FOLDS, shuffle=True, random_state=SEED) for fold, (_, val_idx) in enumerate(skf.split(train_df, train_df["PatientID"])): train_df.loc[val_idx, "fold"] = fold # Image transformations with fixed size train_transform = transforms.Compose( [ transforms.Resize((IMG_SIZE, IMG_SIZE)), transforms.RandomHorizontalFlip(), transforms.RandomRotation(10), transforms.ToTensor(), transforms.Normalize(mean=[0.485, 0.456, 0.406], std=[0.229, 0.224, 0.225]), ] ) test_transform = transforms.Compose( [ transforms.Resize((IMG_SIZE, IMG_SIZE)), transforms.ToTensor(), transforms.Normalize(mean=[0.485, 0.456, 0.406], std=[0.229, 0.224, 0.225]), ] ) class ChestXRayDataset(Dataset): def __init__(self, df, img_dir, transform=None): self.df = df self.img_dir = img_dir self.transform = transform self.labels = df.iloc[:, 1:12].values.astype(np.float32) def __len__(self): return len(self.df) def __getitem__(self, idx): img_path = os.path.join( self.img_dir, self.df.iloc[idx]["StudyInstanceUID"] + ".jpg" ) try: image = Image.open(img_path).convert("RGB") except: image = Image.new("RGB", (IMG_SIZE, IMG_SIZE)) if self.transform: image = self.transform(image) return image, torch.tensor(self.labels[idx], dtype=torch.float32) class EfficientNetModel(nn.Module): def __init__(self): super().__init__() self.base = timm.create_model("tf_efficientnet_b4", pretrained=True) self.classifier = nn.Linear(self.base.classifier.in_features, 11) def forward(self, x): features = self.base.forward_features(x) features = nn.functional.adaptive_avg_pool2d(features, (1, 1)).flatten(1) return self.classifier(features) def train_model(fold): train_fold = train_df[train_df["fold"] != fold].reset_index(drop=True) valid_fold = train_df[train_df["fold"] == fold].reset_index(drop=True) train_ds = ChestXRayDataset(train_fold, "./input/train", train_transform) valid_ds = ChestXRayDataset(valid_fold, "./input/train", test_transform) train_loader = DataLoader( train_ds, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE, shuffle=True, num_workers=4, pin_memory=True ) valid_loader = DataLoader( valid_ds, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE, num_workers=4, pin_memory=True ) model = EfficientNetModel().cuda() criterion = nn.BCEWithLogitsLoss() optimizer = optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=1e-4) best_score = 0 for epoch in range(EPOCHS): model.train() for images, labels in tqdm(train_loader): images, labels = images.cuda(), labels.cuda() optimizer.zero_grad() outputs = model(images) loss = criterion(outputs, labels) loss.backward() optimizer.step() model.eval() valid_preds = [] valid_targets = [] with torch.no_grad(): for images, labels in valid_loader: outputs = model(images.cuda()).sigmoid().cpu().numpy() valid_preds.append(outputs) valid_targets.append(labels.numpy()) valid_preds = np.concatenate(valid_preds) valid_targets = np.concatenate(valid_targets) auc_scores = [ roc_auc_score(valid_targets[:, i], valid_preds[:, i]) for i in range(11) ] mean_auc = np.mean(auc_scores) print(f"Fold {fold} Epoch {epoch}: Validation AUC = {mean_auc:.4f}") if mean_auc > best_score: best_score = mean_auc torch.save(model.state_dict(), f"./working/fold{fold}_best.pth") return best_score # Cross-validation fold_scores = [] for fold in range(FOLDS): score = train_model(fold) fold_scores.append(score) print(f"Fold {fold} Best AUC: {score:.4f}") print(f"Mean CV AUC: {np.mean(fold_scores):.4f}") # Inference with sorted test files class TestDataset(Dataset): def __init__(self, img_dir, transform=None): self.img_dir = img_dir self.files = sorted([f for f in os.listdir(img_dir) if f.endswith(".jpg")]) self.transform = transform def __len__(self): return len(self.files) def __getitem__(self, idx): img_path = os.path.join(self.img_dir, self.files[idx]) try: image = Image.open(img_path).convert("RGB") except: image = Image.new("RGB", (IMG_SIZE, IMG_SIZE)) if self.transform: image = self.transform(image) return image, self.files[idx].replace(".jpg", "") test_ds = TestDataset("./input/test", test_transform) test_loader = DataLoader(test_ds, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE, num_workers=4, shuffle=False) final_preds = [] model_paths = [f"./working/fold{i}_best.pth" for i in range(FOLDS)] with torch.no_grad(): for model_path in model_paths: model = EfficientNetModel().cuda() model.load_state_dict(torch.load(model_path)) model.eval() fold_preds = [] ids = [] for images, study_ids in tqdm(test_loader): outputs = model(images.cuda()).sigmoid().cpu().numpy() fold_preds.append(outputs) ids.extend(study_ids) fold_preds = np.concatenate(fold_preds) final_preds.append(fold_preds) # Ensemble and save final_preds = np.mean(final_preds, axis=0) sub_cols = [ "ETT - Abnormal", "ETT - Borderline", "ETT - Normal", "NGT - Abnormal", "NGT - Borderline", "NGT - Incompletely Imaged", "NGT - Normal", "CVC - Abnormal", "CVC - Borderline", "CVC - Normal", "Swan Ganz Catheter Present", ] submission = pd.DataFrame({"StudyInstanceUID": ids}) submission[sub_cols] = final_preds os.makedirs("./submission", exist_ok=True) submission.to_csv("./submission/submission.csv", index=False) print("Submission saved successfully!")
